    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Those who submit bids to a prime contractor, subcontractor, or prime bidder, often for materials or labor on a construction project.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
